{"tid":2124572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】鄧達智初步確診 曾到新城港台開咪","createTime":"2020-07-25T13:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T13:05:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40e61dfc16458b757a010df0a2eb170c844dc359","tid":2124572,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200725/Z4TTNX57JW2BUAVC6VVCMGDU2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200725%2FZ4TTNX57JW2BUAVC6VVCMGDU2Y%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHXjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=2761c0d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200725%2FZ4TTNX57JW2BUAVC6VVCMGDU2Y%2F&h=37a0c29a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200725/Z4TTNX57JW2BUAVC6VVCMGDU2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】鄧達智初步確診 曾到新城港台開咪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新增回應及內容】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【鹽可殺菌？】網傳施匡翹住院要求膳食加鹽 經理人：家人畀咗好大包 <br />\n<br />\n62歲的香港知名時裝設計師鄧達智今日初步確診武漢肺炎，目前在家自行隔離等待醫院床位。由於鄧達智間中會到各電台開咪或受訪，他指未知自己是經由新城群組或三聯PR群組染疫，目前只能先在家休息，等待進一步化驗結果。據知，鄧達智的老公目前並未有染上武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n鄧達智證實初步確診，他接受電話訪問時，語調正常不覺有喘氣，他表示剛量完體溫，是36.5度，現在元朗家中自我隔離：「我係星期一發覺自己唔舒服，以為中暑，都唔知有事，冇特別理，後來有幾聲咳，有少少發燒，醫生朋友後來嚟我屋企幫我做test ，昨晚就初步確診，而Clement（老公）就陰性，冇事。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【新城冷清】范振鋒帶齊口罩手套返台直播 拍檔薛家燕家中冇罩開咪<br />\n<br />\n鄧達智指自己上周六（18日）返了新城錄音做節目，之後再去了三聯的網台接受訪問，「因為新城有好多錄音室，三聯個女仔PR又係後來確診，..................................<br />\n<br />\n他指醫務衞生署指他病況不嚴重，加上未有床位，着他先留家中隔離，再等安排作進一步確診。.......................................................<br />\n<br />\n網上亦流傳消息指，鄧達智上周四（16日）在港台主持節目《講東講西》，曾除下口罩，同一節目的 馬恩賜及劉天蘭，曾與鄧達智除罩合照。..............................................<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n打國際線 《蘋果》英文版免費試睇 按此了解更多<br />\n英文版已登錄新版《蘋果》App按此下載/更新<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F1gwuyhdDB_pL4Kt_VfJ8jtpHIE=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6DV3LPTJAYCRKFIULQDMEM7RNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF1gwuyhdDB_pL4Kt_VfJ8jtpHIE%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6DV3LPTJAYCRKFIULQDMEM7RNU.jpg&h=cdb58eb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SuW_ViFq1ZXcRfZYPbjZLjRhVNM=/640x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CWHKPQD7EIHMFLCUHHWBYQA4SA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSuW_ViFq1ZXcRfZYPbjZLjRhVNM%3D%2F640x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCWHKPQD7EIHMFLCUHHWBYQA4SA.jpg&h=510a6a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧達智證實初步確診，他接受電話訪問時，語調正常不覺有喘氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wEIzcqbVne5XBS-eVKXb-U7eftI=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PHUURXCTCOESC43XRDPYWCIWFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwEIzcqbVne5XBS-eVKXb-U7eftI%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPHUURXCTCOESC43XRDPYWCIWFY.jpg&h=5a20e490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上周工作頻頻，上周六他亦曾接受三聯旗下的網上平台《一本》主持人米哈訪問。"}]}